  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 94d143587ba84ee4b8e4fa2245b5301c, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::TutorialManager
  tutorialText: {fileID: 722622487}
  dialogues:
  - Hello!
  - I'm here!
  - I heard about treasure box, so I'm going to start my journey to find treasure!
  - So now we need to go to get treasure map!
  - But there are many scary monsters... like that birds.
  - They are very dangerous, so we have to avoid them.
  - But we have a magic function wand!
  - You only have the Linear Wand right now. Try plotting a point to go get the map!
  - Find other wands later to create paths with more advanced functions!
  - Tap this button to switch between your acquired wands.
  - Check the available wands list here and plan your path carefully!
  - If a monster hits you along the way...
  - ...you'll lose one of your <b>Hearts</b> up here! Watch out!
  - Running low on health? You'll need to clear a Heart Stage to recover.
  - See this <b><color=#FF0000>Heart icon</color></b>?
  - Collect it to enter a special Heart Stage!
  - This is a <b>Coin</b>.
  - Collect enough, and you might be able to buy something cool at the shop...?
  - Lastly, see the <b>STOP LEFT</b> counter here?
  - Left-click to draw your path, and Right-click to stop mid-flight.
  - <b>STOP LEFT</b> shows how many times you can stop.
  - Once it hits zero, you can't stop and must keep moving forward.
  - Plan your strategy carefully and get that treasure!
  - Before to start our journey, let's practice how to use wands!
  stepEffects:
  - {fileID: 0}
  - {fileID: 1621806507}
